# Tauri / Rust build artifacts — regenerated by `cargo`/`tauri build`.
# NEVER commit: src-tauri/target alone is ~3GB.
src-tauri/target/
src-tauri/gen/

# Node (tauri-cli + e2e harness deps)
node_modules/

# E2E run artifacts (isolated WebView2 user-data / logs / reports — all reproducible)
e2e/runs/
e2e/reports/
e2e/rwd-runs/
e2e-screenshot*.png

# The runnable shell binary is NOT committed (a 17MB blob doesn't belong in git).
# Produce it on a NON-WDAC machine with scripts\win\build-shell.bat
# (cargo build --release → copy into prebuilt\), then copy the exe to this box.
# WDAC (enforced) blocks a local cargo rebuild here, but running an existing/
# copied-in unsigned exe works — so keep a prebuilt copy on disk, just not in git.
# See prebuilt\README.md.
prebuilt/*.exe
